{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Goldenheart</i> is an old-school style linear fantasy adventure game created by two people. It has a look and feel inspired by our favorite classic console games and a surreal fantasy setting like no other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002500/extras/GifHistahnia.gif?t=1735426378\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as an outsider, learning the ancient lore of a foreign land as you solve a mystery that has recently befallen it. As you progress you\u2019ll find new tools and ideas that will augment the gameplay while leading you into more dangerous and anomalous places.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002500/extras/GifTuld.gif?t=1735426378\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019ll need to take time to explore and observe your surroundings in order to navigate the world and solve puzzles related to the plot and lore. You\u2019ll master simple but dynamic combat using targeting, dodging, and a shield, while managing your quiver capacity and stamina. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002500/extras/GifKahlora.gif?t=1735426378\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Quick Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feature length adventure game in the old-school spirit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Compelling story and environmental storytelling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keyboard/Mouse + Full xbox controller support<i>*</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The difficulty settings only effect combat damage, keeping the emphasis on exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Linear narrative that keeps moving forward</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Streamlined gameplay without boring filler or menu diving</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Minimal system requirements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All content originates from our home studio with zero use of AI</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>*Other controllers will work but the button icon might be wrong.</i></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ready for Action","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3002500/d4f7ede5dbeb8f8865f4ea3fd7d02d7388d24479.jpg"},{"name":"Tuldenorrea 101","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3002500/a833da1717848070248f8605280e28530aa10494.jpg"},{"name":"Philologist's Apprentice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3002500/9701c1216d517b67cedd7ae2772ab688bd67284e.jpg"},{"name":"Molekin Slayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3002500/d823ed7133b2f264e59ae3cdf5f4d8b14cf2a134.jpg"},{"name":"Now Accepting Volunteers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3002500/5fc423db75fc4582da53ebb27f5c0e76499596ed.jpg"},{"name":"Alpine Rescue","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3002500/6ab5f933d11e409c38a9bad3be91cdea11321d11.jpg"},{"name":"This is definitely 100% a good idea.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3002500/c9a259ecf008981d040793f53ab831f6fcfee16c.jpg"},{"name":"Holekin Slayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3002500/f561462e6ac44e26aa82e8ec51ef5c5e8605e80c.jpg"},{"name":"Nark Slayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3002500/5b0ed0435cf99a6e6c92912f095b329aa6a876d9.jpg"},{"name":"Rusty Knight","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3002500/02729d7e97845e891c907f08c63ad7bff0468cec.jpg"}],"total":54},"background":"ht